### 02. 타 멤버 권한/직책 수정 (LEADER/ADMIN 전용)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/v1/workspaces/{{workspacePublicId}}/projects/{{projectPublicId}}/members/{{targetUserPublicId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newPosition": "프론트엔드 개발자",
  "newRole": "MEMBER"
}

### 04. 내 프로젝트 멤버 정보 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectPublicId}}/members/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 05. 내 직책 수정
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectPublicId}}/members/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newPosition": "풀스택 개발자"
}